WEBVTT

00:02.918 --> 00:04.452
- Oh, God.
- Hey, Boo-boo bear.

00:04.718 --> 00:06.052
What did you
just call me?

00:06.086 --> 00:07.503
- Boo-boo bear.
- Oh.

00:07.537 --> 00:09.672
It's one of several nicknames
I made up for you,

00:09.706 --> 00:11.674
and you can choose which one
you like best,

00:11.708 --> 00:13.426
'cause I want this
to be a give and take.

00:13.477 --> 00:16.512
Okay, we went out once,
and nothing happened.

00:16.546 --> 00:18.347
There is no "this."

00:18.382 --> 00:19.732
We have "cookie tush"...

00:19.766 --> 00:21.317
Wow, just
right out the gate.

00:21.351 --> 00:23.352
"Winnie the boo,"
"Lady presh-presh,"

00:23.387 --> 00:25.955
"Ann-Berry sauce,"
"Annie get your boo,"

00:25.989 --> 00:28.357
"Tommy's girl,"
"Annie banannie--"

00:28.391 --> 00:30.109
Hey!

00:30.160 --> 00:32.411
All right,
let's do this.

00:34.765 --> 00:37.116
What are you doing?

00:37.167 --> 00:39.769
Is this not
one of those?

00:39.803 --> 00:41.070
I might have misread the vibe.

00:41.088 --> 00:44.307
Oh, my God, dude, you have
to be cooler about this.

00:44.341 --> 00:46.742
Look, I told Leslie
because she's my best friend,

00:46.760 --> 00:49.295
but if anybody finds out
about this

00:49.346 --> 00:50.513
and they start jabbering,

00:50.547 --> 00:52.748
it's gonna make it
really hard to know

00:52.766 --> 00:54.784
if this is
actually anything,

00:54.818 --> 00:58.454
so just keep it
on the DL, okay?

00:58.488 --> 01:00.640
I feel like
you're embarrassed by me.

01:00.691 --> 01:01.757
That is accurate.

01:02.275 --> 01:03.609
Can I at least change
my Facebook status

01:03.644 --> 01:04.760
to "In a relationship"?

01:04.778 --> 01:06.228
Definitely not.

01:06.262 --> 01:07.229
"It's complicated"?

01:08.263 --> 01:09.114
Whatever.

01:09.115 --> 01:11.133
Am I in a relationship?

01:13.236 --> 01:14.837
It's complicated.

